         Just wanted to make something clear in my post.  Killing the quest giver restarts the three spawn process.  I received the Symbol from the third spawn, after killing the quest giver.  The quest giver does not in fact drop the symbol, as I implied.</P><P>Series of events...</P><P>Turned in symbol...<BR>Killed three triggered spawns...<BR>Looted symbol from third mob...<BR>Killed quest giver...<BR>Upon his death, three triggered spawns re-popped...<BR>Looted symbol from third spawn...</P><P>understand?</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
